model.name: Pool Pillow Flat Comfort Mule
model.disambiguatingDescription: This reinterpretation of the Pool Pillow flat comfort mule was inspired by Louis Vuitton's Spring-Summer 2022 fashion show. The adjustable, padded front strap comes in satin with polka dots, a key theme of the collection. The comfort of this model is further enhanced by its anatomic footbed.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• White / Black
  • Satin
  • Down filling
  • Velcro strap
  • Anatomic insole
  • Treaded micro outsole
  • LV Circle on the strap
  • Made in Italy
